    # game/areas/galerocks02npcs.rpy:448
    old "“What does {i}she{/i} think?” He looks at you as if you’re mad, then glances at the nearby fishers. “She’d be heartbroken to realize she’s soul-le... I mean, spell-less. I won’t tell her unless I have no other way. She’s merely a child. I’m doing what’s best for her.” "
