    # game/areas/galerocks02npcs.rpy:481
    old "“I’ve asked our sorcerers about what they felt when they used the stones. Their pneuma got stronger than on most days, and nothing bad happened to them. We risk nothing, {i}outsider{/i},” he says, with growing irritation, and stops himself from scratching the scars on his neck. "
