    # game/areas/galerocks02npcs.rpy:514
    old "“Have you heard about the previous roadwarden? {color=#f6d6bd}Asterion{/color}?” You nod. “In spring, I sent him to one of the greatest mages in the peninsula, some druid, I think, and that old prick told me there was nothing he could do, you hear that? And I had {i}paid{/i} the messenger to learn this!” He squeezes his cloak even tighter to his side. “We have no herbalists here, but since the spirit rocks are safe, I’d rather spend my last coins for such a chance than try nothing and regret it.” "
    new ""

