    old "“And what would be a {i}usual{/i} name in the city? A {i}builder{/i}?” After your shrug, {color=#f6d6bd}Iuno{/color} grasps one of her wooden blocks like a dagger. “Our forebears used to, ehm, {i}dig{/i} in rocks, widening the caves, and it was a name with great honor behind it. When I look around,” she does so, as to prove her point, “it reminds me of our long path. From hiding, to thriving, and on the surface.” She can’t hide her smile. "
